ok<\/i>.","Double cream with <b>48% fat<b> or whipping cream with <b>35% fat<b> are both suitable for this recipe.","If time allows, return the salmon in puff pastry to the fridge for <b>30 minutes<b> before baking. This will ensure an even bake.","The salmon in puff pastry can be made ahead of time and frozen uncooked. Use within <b>2 weeks.<b>","Adjust cooking time in <b>step 11<b> according to time indicated on rice packet.","This pastry log encases a classic, creamy salmon and dill filling. Served with a simple lemon-flavoured risotto, this is an impressive main course for a weekend dinner party.","For extra flavour, add <b>¼ tsp<b> cayenne pepper to the salmon filling in <b>step 4.<b>"],"basicInfo":["easy","25m","45m","6 portions"]}